00:46:55,345 --> 00:46:56,505
Hei.

598
00:46:57,480 --> 00:47:00,415
Kau tak apa-apa? /
Aku perlu bicara denganmu.

599
00:47:01,684 --> 00:47:03,083
Ya, masuklah.

