655
00:51:16,105 --> 00:51:17,629
<i>Apakah Sara bersamamu?</i>

656
00:51:18,007 --> 00:51:19,304
Persetan Alex.

657
00:51:20,143 --> 00:51:21,132
<i>Tidak!</i>

658
00:51:21,344 --> 00:51:22,402
Tunggu sebentar.

659
00:51:30,086 --> 00:51:31,610
<i>Telepon Masuk
Alex Layton</i>

660
00:51:40,062 --> 00:51:41,723
Pulanglah!

