671
00:52:37,653 --> 00:52:38,881
Lucu juga.

672
00:52:40,223 --> 00:52:44,060
Aku tak sangka Eric tipe pria
yang meniduri gadis baru...

673
00:52:44,060 --> 00:52:46,927
